 Sign-ups for American Roundball Corp. spring development leagues are scheduled 
for 7 p.m. Tuesday at Nogales High. Individual or team registration will be 
taken for boys' varsity, junior varsity and seventh- and eighth-grade leagues, 
and girls' varsity leagues. Information: (818) 995-3761. GARY KLEIN 
</P>
