 San Clemente 3, Marina 0 -- Gabe Gardner had 14 kills at Marina to lead San 
Clemente, 15-11, 15-13, 15-8, to its third consecutive victory. San Clemente is 
3-0. 
</P>
<P>
 Fountain Valley 3, Mission Viejo 0 -- Phil Domingo had a game-high 14 kills to 
lead Fountain Valley (2-0), 15-6, 15-10, 15-13, over Mission Viejo. 
