Housing and Urban Development office of San Francisco for real estate asset 
management in Orange County. 
</P>
<P>
 * Morton Electronic Materials of Tustin won a $276,037 contract from the Naval 
Air Warfare Center of Indianapolis, Ind., for electrical and electronic 
equipment components. 
