<TEXT>
<P>
 A 28-year-old youth group leader at a church has been arrested on suspicion of 
molesting four boys between 1991 and 1993, police said Wednesday. 
</P>
<P>
 Michael Webb Blinkhorn of Reseda was arrested Tuesday on suspicion of 18 
felony counts of child molestation, according to Corinne Loomis of the 
Placentia Police Department. 
</P>
