</P>
<P>
 American Red Cross Earthquake Victims Fund will be the recipient of $10,500 
raised by Los Angeles Club Med World Expo at the Museum of Flying in Santa 
Monica on Feb. 1. The funds were proceeds of a silent auction of vacation 
trips. Host was Jean-Michel Ladau, president and CEO of Club Med Sales Inc. 
</P>
<P>
