its Emergency Earthquake Relief Fund. Agencies benefiting are Friends of the 
Family, Koryo Health Foundation, Los Angeles Commission on Assaults Against 
Women, Mary Magdalene Project, National Council of Negro Women/San Fernando 
Valley, Ocean Park Community Center for its Turning Point Shelter, San Fernando 
Valley Neighborhood Legal Services Inc., Senior Health and Peer Counseling, 
Valley Trauma Center, Venice Family Clinic, Westside Women's Health Center and 
Wise Senior Services. 
