<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Joan of Arc -- A recent review in Ventura County Life of the musical "Joan of 
Arc" stated that "little remains of the original libretto by Susan Stewart 
Potter." Upon re-examination, this statement requires amplification. According 
to director John Blondell and composer David Potter, revisions were made to the 
libretto, but both stated that this is part of the normal development process 
and that Susan Stewart Potter collaborated in that process at every stage and 
deserves full credit as author of the libretto in its current form. 
</P>
</TEXT>
