<P>
 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 12-13 05,20,05,06,05,20 RETURNING STARTERS YR. POS. B-T 
Keith Bigelow Jr. P/OF R-L Johnny Matlock Sr. SS R-R Aristeo Rodriguez Sr. C 
R-R Sean Sears Sr. OF R-R Jeff Sorensen Sr. P R-R Jorge Valles Sr. Inf B-R TOP 
