<P>
 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 148-105 04,20,05,06,05 RETURNING STARTERS YR. POS. B-T Jim 
Brewer Sr. P/1B L-L Craig Daedelow Sr. SS R-R Bryce Dillard Sr. P L-L Brad 
Lineberger Jr. 2B R-R Scott Palmer Sr. Util R-R Jeremy Vidales So. 3B R-R Chris 
Yadrick Sr. OF R-R TOP RETURNERS YR. POS. B-T None TOP NEWCOMERS YR. POS. B-T 
John Church Jr. P L-L Ryan Evans Jr. P R-R Rick Parie Sr. P/1B L-L Jason Segal 
Sr. OF L-L Luke Woodfin Sr. C B-R OUTLOOK 
